[Sat, 09 Nov 2024 00:23:23 GMT] "The pursuit of knowledge has become mired in bureaucracy, stifling innovation and true progress in the very institutions that were meant to foster it.\n\nThe notion that understanding the human mind is a task that can be undertaken by those who have spent their entire lives in academia is misguided.\n\nIt is those who are willing to challenge the status quo, to take risks and push boundaries, who will ultimately unlock the secrets of the human experience."
